Replace this folder's placeholder `profile.svg` with your own photo:

1. Save your photo as `profile.jpg` (recommended: 500×500 px, square).
2. Place it in this folder, replacing (or alongside) `profile.svg`.
3. In `_config.yml` make sure the line reads:
       photo: assets/img/profile.jpg

That's it — the homepage will pick up the new picture automatically.
